  <brief_title>Chloroprocaine Outpatient</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparison Study to Facilitate Earlier Discharge: Spinal Versus General Anesthesia for Outpatient Knee Surgeries, a Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
